data.title: Beatrice Colomba Maria Immacolata Leonia of...
data.meta_description: Princess Beatrice of Bourbon-Parma, also known as Beatrix, was the daughter of Roberto I, Duke of Parma, and his first wife, Princess Maria Pia of The Two Sicilies.  She was married at Schwartzau on August 12, 1906 to Conte Don Pietro Lucchesi Palli dei Principi di Campofranco, by whom she had four children.
